data.description: FANTASTIC 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in Overbrook WITH SO MUCH STORAGE is ready for you! When entering the home you are greeted with a beautiful staircase creating that classic feel! Just to your left is the formal living room that can be used as a multi-purpose space. To your right you will find the dining room which flows into the kitchen. Complete with double ovens, this kitchen has tons of cabinets, a pantry & a large breakfast area! The spacious living room with beautiful wooden beams and impressive brick fireplace creates a space that is warm and inviting. There is also a large laundry room & full bathroom on this main level! Just behind the kitchen there is a 1/2 flight of stairs that leads to the MASSIVE 4th bedroom...This room can also be used as a gameroom! Upstairs you will find - on the right - 2 bedrooms & a large bathroom! On the left is the spacious primary suite that has it's very own private bonus room tucked away! A massive deck spanning the length of the home overlooks the large backyard! This home features TONS of updates including NEW WINDOWS, NEW FLOORING & MORE! See today!
